    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206450/extras/a3480efe74f3ff69730baf2d3cce50ee.poster.avif?t=1760249588\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206450/extras/a3480efe74f3ff69730baf2d3cce50ee.webm?t=1760249588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206450/extras/a3480efe74f3ff69730baf2d3cce50ee.mp4?t=1760249588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>矮人是一个基于逻辑的2d益智游戏，你控制一个小队的两个矮人导航通过奸诈的洞穴寻找黄金。 一个矮人所采取的每一步都反映了另一个矮人的运动，这使得时间和计划对于成功至关重要。 洞穴里充满了尖刺，骷髅和其他陷阱，迫使你思考几个动作，以确保两个矮人逃脱安然无恙。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206450/extras/3f7ec25f725345352041de4ed85c8f3b.poster.avif?t=1760249588\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206450/extras/3f7ec25f725345352041de4ed85c8f3b.webm?t=1760249588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206450/extras/3f7ec25f725345352041de4ed85c8f3b.mp4?t=1760249588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>主要特点:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>两个字符的同步运动，增加深度的拼图机制。<br></li><li>众多的水平，增加了难度和新的挑战。<br></li><li>各种致命的陷阱和敌人智胜。<br></li><li>独特的游戏需要战略思维和远见.<br></li><li>具有挑战性的难题与后果的一举一动。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206450/extras/63dfbffc526e987e66c4a31edad400e6.avif?t=1760249588\" width=600 height=200 /></span>",
